sequenceDiagram
    participant User as ユーザー
    participant Router as router.php
    participant PageController as PageController
    participant JSON as pages.json
    participant Template as auth/login_form.php

    User->>Router: /index.php?page=login にアクセス（GET）
    Router->>Router: 認証チェック（public_pages に含まれる）
    Router->>PageController: render("login") を呼び出し

    PageController->>JSON: pages.json を読み込む
    JSON-->>PageController: "auth/login_form.php" を返す

    PageController->>Template: login_form.php を include
    Template-->>PageController: HTML（body 部分）を返す

    PageController->>User: header.php + login_form.php + footer.php を出力